data.description: Older Well-Established Subdivision! Large 1/2 acre lot with, Covered Front Porch.  Entering into Foyer area with a Living Room and Separate Dining Room.  Open Kitchen/Family Room with Gas Fireplace.  Engineered Laminate Wood Floors.  Upstairs there are 2 bedrooms with bath BUT the finished basement offers Large Bedroom with Bath and there is another room that could be another bedroom if needed or playroom, office, etc whatever meets your needs.  Storage Building to remain!  Must SEE!
